{"article_id":"NzLvjuiM0qI4cuHP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The conclusion of Special Counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"- and its determination","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that no evidence supports claims of Trump-Russia collusion -","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"has spurred calls from President Trump ' s allies to closely examine the probe ' s origins at the FBI .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Trump , for his part , called to \" look into \" those","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"who had created a \" false narrative \"","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"sparking the investigation .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Senate Judiciary Committee Chairman Lindsey Graham , R-S.C. , has already vowed to look into the FBI ' s actions .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Here are just seven FBI actions and comments ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"covered in controversial text messages ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that have raised questions about the impartiality of the probe .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"On Aug. 8 , 2016 , FBI lawyer Lisa Page texted her lover , Peter Strzok ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"who was in charge of the FBI investigation of Hillary Clinton","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"and later worked on the Russia probe :","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"`` [ Trump 's ] not ever going to become president , right ?","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"Right ? ! ''","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Strzok responded on his FBI-issued work phone :","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"`` No .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"No he wo n't .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"We 'll stop it . ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"The text was discovered by the inspector general at the U.S. Department of Justice ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"after the FBI failed to uncover the message on its own .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"\" It is not only indicative of a biased state of mind","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"but , even more seriously , implies a willingness","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"to take official action","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"to impact the presidential candidate ' s electoral prospects , \"","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"the IG report stated .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"The inspector general ' s office also asked Strzok for his response .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" When asked about this text message ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"Strzok stated","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"that he did not specifically recall sending it ,","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"but that he believed","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"that it was intended to reassure Page","depth":16},{"id":33,"text":"that Trump would not be elected ,","depth":16},{"id":34,"text":"not to suggest","depth":16},{"id":35,"text":"that he would do something","depth":17},{"id":36,"text":"to impact the investigation , \"","depth":17},{"id":37,"text":"the report notes .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Strzok later told the House Judiciary Committee","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that he meant","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Americans in general would stop Trump in 2016 .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Strzok calls Russia investigation an ' insurance policy '","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"in case Trump wins","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"In an Aug. 15 , 2016 text message , Strzok told Page :","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"`` I want to believe ...","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"that there 's no way","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"Trump gets elected","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"but I 'm afraid","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"e ca n't take that risk .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"t 's like an insurance policy in the unlikely event","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"ou die","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"efore you 're 40 . ''","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"ritics say","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"he text implies","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"trzok wanted the investigation to hurt Trump","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"n case he were to win .","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"trzok told the IG and the House Judiciary Committee","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"hat his text meant","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"n investigation should happen right away .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"My use of the phrase ' insurance policy ' was simply to say ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"hile the polls or people might think","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"t is less likely that then-candidate Trump would be elected ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"hat should not influence ... us doing our job responsibly , \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"trzok told the House Judiciary Committee .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"trzok admits in 2017","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"there 's no big there there ' on Russian collusion","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"espite having called the Russia situation an \" insurance policy \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"nd having pressed for more vigorous investigation ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"text from May 17 , 2017 shows","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"trzok had doubts .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"n texts to Page , Strzok questioned","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"hether he should join Mueller ' s team","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"nvestigating Trump and Russia","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"ecause : `` you and I both know","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"he odds are nothing .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"f I thought","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"t was likely","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"'d be there no question .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"hesitate in part","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"ecause of my gut sense and concern","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"here 's no big there there . ''","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"sked by the inspector general about this text ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"trzok said","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"e was merely questioning","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"hether collusion was coordinated","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"r just involved \" a bunch of opportunists . \"","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"trzok ultimately joined the team","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"nvestigating Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"efore being removed","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"nd then fired ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"fter the IG report revealed his texts .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"BI lawyer suggests","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"a","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"small team interview Clinton b","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"cause ' she might be our next president ' I","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"February 2016 , w","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"ile Hillary Clinton was under investigation for improper handling of classified information , t","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"e Department of Justice wanted to send four attorneys t","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"question Clinton . B","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"t FBI attorney Page urged both Strzok and then-FBI Deputy Director Andrew McCabe to only allow two DOJ people to be sent . \"","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"Our best reason t","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"hold the line at 2 and 2 i","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":": S","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"e might be our next president , \" P","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"ge explained to McCabe via text . \"","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"The last thing w","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"need is us going in there l","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"aded for bear , w","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"en it is not operationally necessary ... T","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"is is as much about reputational protection as anything . \" T","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"e inspector general ' s office asked Page about that a","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"d reported t","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"at she told them \"","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"while ' it ' s irrelevant w","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"ether or not [ Clinton ] ... would or would not become president ... i","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"she did become president , I","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"don ' t want her left with a feeling t","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"at ... the FBI marched in with an army of 50 i","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"order to interview me . ' \" P","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"ge and others did not appear to express similar concern about Trump ' s feelings o","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"ce his turn for investigation came . U","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"timately , all four DOJ prosecutors were allowed to interview Clinton , w","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"o brought nine of her own lawyers to the interview . T","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"e inspector general also found several pro-Clinton texts t","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"at other FBI employees sent from work phones , f","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"om \" I ' m with her , \" to quips a","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"out being \" done interviewing the President \" -","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"even though Clinton had not won the election yet . M","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Cabe compares Trump to ' Mafia ' f","depth":6},{"id":129,"text":"r asking i","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"he should give speech to FBI M","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"Cabe , in his book and in press summaries , said t","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"at Trump asked him w","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"ether he should give a speech to FBI agents a","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"ter James Comey had been fired as FBI director a","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"d when McCabe was filling in for him . T","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"ump asked both McCabe and his chief counsel Don McGahn i","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"such a speech would be helpful . W","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"ile McCabe says h","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"told Trump s","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"ch a speech would be fine , h","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"later wrote t","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"at Trump ' s question really reminded him of `` a case i","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"volving the Russian Mafia , w","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"en I sent a man I","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"' ll call Big Felix in t","depth":15},{"id":146,"text":"meet with a Mafia boss ... T","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"e same kind of thing was happening here . '' \"","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"The president and his men were trying to work me the way a","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"criminal brigade would operate , \" M","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"Cabe added . T","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"e inspector general report found an exchange between FBI employees on their work phones from Nov. 9 , just after the election . \"","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"That makes me even more sad ... I","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"can ' t stop stressing about what I could have done differently , \" a","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"unidentified FBI attorney replied . F","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"I employee calls Trump supporters ' all poor to middle class , ' ' lazy POS ' T","depth":5},{"id":156,"text":"e same FBI employee w","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"o discussed crying after the election a","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"so used an FBI-issued device t","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"direct class-based disdain toward Trump supporters : \"","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"Trump ' s supporters are all poor to middle class , uneducated , lazy POS t","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"at think h","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"will magically grant them jobs f","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"r doing nothing . \" P","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"ter Strzok used similar language , s","depth":7},{"id":165,"text":"ying in one text : \"","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"Just went to a southern Virginia Walmart . I","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"could SMELL the Trump support .... \" M","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"xim Lott is Executive Producer of Stossel TV and creator of ElectionBettingOdds.com . H","depth":2},{"id":169,"text":"can be reached on Twitter at @ MaximLott .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":339,"left":337,"right":338,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":337,"left":260,"right":336,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":177,"righ